                <p>Our iceshrimp instance "social.joshrandall.net" has now moved to <a class="link" href="https://joshrandall.social">joshrandall.social</a>.</p>
                <p>If you have an account, all of your data should still be intact.</p>
                <br>
                <a class="button" style="font-size:2em;" href="https://joshrandall.social">Go there now</a>
            </div>
            
        </section>
                
    
<!-- <hr> -->
    </main>
